We’re having a short on CTRE Power Distribution Pannel 40 amp breaker circuit. Listening to the breaker, it sounds like it is resetting every couple of seconds.

Is this configurable so that when the breaker trips, it does not automagically resets and it takes operator intervention to turn it back on?

-Thanks

-Mike

Sounds like you’ve got a short to hunt down.
